data.text:
@DrJinRussell Nigel seems to think 1% is fearmongering, but other paeds find it reassuringly low. 

Separate from the uncertainty around the true value (likely lower now anyhow) it's interesting how little consensus there is on what a "good" number would be. 

https://t.co/T3rmR2ba45

@DrJinRussell The 1% hospitalisation percentage as misinformation story is interesting. 

Back in Jan an NCIRS group estimated it was about 1.2% in Oz (Delta wave), which I thought that was a bit higher than expected, others were reassured by how low it was. 

https://t.co/EXPLwWPBA7

@DrJinRussell sounds good.
believe this will be a talking point in future seminars.

https://t.co/3LeCFCysZa
